<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="20Aug1937"><font color="red">20 August 1937</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): [??] - Gorky - Soviet = Big Bright Boost K.O. Please take when in my flat book on S. Pat and Boulogne and forward to me registered. What about the dictionary! French-Russian wd do as well &hellip; what about the weekly <i>Irish Times</i>? We may move back to Basel in a few days to spend a week there or may not. It is only 16 Km. </div>
